#****** sge_queue/enable_queue() ******
# 
#  NAME
#     enable_queue -- enable queuelist
#
#  SYNOPSIS
#     enable_queue { queue } 
#
#  FUNCTION
#     This procedure enables a given queuelist by calling the qmod -e binary
#
